About.Name: Binh Truong
About.AboutText:
Hello, my name is Binh Truong. I am a dedicated Computer Science undergraduate at Seattle Pacific University with a strong passion for software development. I am constantly working to expand my technical skill set, with a current focus on C++ programming.

I enjoy tackling complex programming challenges and thrive in collaborative environments where I can both contribute my expertise and learn from my peers.

Beyond the classroom, I stay engaged with the tech community through hackathons, coding competitions, and open-source projects. I strongly believe in continuous learning and am always looking for opportunities to explore new methodologies and technologies.
